*libbufr-000360 (07 Dec 2008)

  07 Dec 2008; Steve Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +libbufr-000360.ebuild:
  New ebuild for the open source BUFR library from ECMWF (requires at least
